		<div class="below-entry-meta"><span class="posted-on"><a href="https://blog.zenika.com/2022/03/18/kubernetes-quest-ce-qui-va-remplacer-les-podsecuritypolicies/" title="12 h 11 min" rel="bookmark"><i class="fa fa-calendar-o"></i> <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2022-03-18T12:11:26+01:00">18 mars 2022</time><time class="updated" datetime="2022-04-13T15:29:36+01:00">13 avril 2022</time></a></span>
